%% Diagram: iTIP / iMIP invitation and RSVP flow
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant O as Organizer
    participant CS as Calendar service
    participant Q as Message queue
    participant Mail as Email worker
    participant A as Attendee MUA

    O->>CS: create event with attendees
    CS->>CS: persist VEVENT (status=confirmed)
    CS->>CS: persist attendees (PARTSTAT=NEEDS-ACTION)
    CS->>Q: enqueue iTIP REQUEST per attendee

    loop per attendee
        Q->>Mail: process job
        Mail->>Mail: build iMIP message - text/calendar method=REQUEST
        Mail->>A: send invitation email
    end

    A->>CS: RSVP - PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED
    CS->>CS: update attendee row, bump SEQUENCE
    CS->>Q: enqueue iTIP REPLY to organizer
    Q->>Mail: deliver REPLY
    Mail->>O: email with response
